---
title: Spiced Beef Tacos & Charred Corn Salsa with Dill-Parsley Mayo Slaw
description: Sometimes it can be tricky to find new ways to jazz up tacos but not tonight - onion chutney on beef is taking out the guesswork and creating new inspiration for your taco night. We also threw in a herby mayo into the slaw for a bit of fun.
